summary: Deku: -tells Bakugo about his secret- All Might: ok, just the three of us will know. no more blabbing. Deku: -tells Todoroki...
body:
Deku: -tells Bakugo about his secret-

All Might: ok, just the three of us will know. no more blabbing.

Deku: -tells Todoroki about his secret and brings him to a meeting-

All Might: fine, it’ll be between us four

Deku: -systematically ends up spilling the beans to each classmate one by one, as well as a few students not even in 1a. invites them to the meetings-

All Might, looking at all of his students crammed together and on each other’s laps and whatnot: midoriya, my boy… this is ridiculous

Deku:

All Might: 

Everyone else:

All Might, sighing in defeat: we’re going to need a bigger meeting room
